        <Parent_String>legs by design [300040866], legs (furniture components) [300162380], furniture legs and leg components [300040822], furniture components [300040215], furnishings components [300241953], components by specific context [300241584], components (objects parts) [300241583], Components (hierarchy name) [300241490], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
